by the recipient and MAY<a id="Appendix_A_Target_25"></a><a aria-label="Product behavior note 25" href="fa61e5fc-f8fb-4d5b-9695-c724af0c3829#Appendix_A_25" data-linktype="relative-path">&lt;25&gt;</a> be set to
arbitrary values upon an update to the <b>supplementalCredentials</b>
attribute.</p><p><b>Reserved2 (1 byte): </b>This value MUST be ignored
by the recipient and MUST be set to zero.</p><p><b>Version (1 byte): </b>This value MUST be set to 1.</p><p><b>NumberOfHashes (1 byte): </b>This value MUST be
set to 29 because there are 29 hashes in the array.</p><p><b>Reserved3 (12 bytes): </b>This value MUST be
ignored by the recipient and MUST be set to zero.</p><p>For information on the <b>Hash</b> fields, see section <span><a href="0705f888-62e1-4a4c-bac0-b4d427f396f8" data-linktype="relative-path">3.1.1.8.11</a></span>.</p></div>